    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>添加到愿望单以在游戏发布时收到通知。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/51f261a8544f03d6d903cc93d3e2ba87.poster.avif?t=1753199962\" width=734 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/51f261a8544f03d6d903cc93d3e2ba87.webm?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/51f261a8544f03d6d903cc93d3e2ba87.mp4?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/f6afa71f69a33507959b841fd09d5177.poster.avif?t=1753199962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/f6afa71f69a33507959b841fd09d5177.webm?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/f6afa71f69a33507959b841fd09d5177.mp4?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/cd90f4ab8d08748bf225cdafa1f9d861.poster.avif?t=1753199962\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/cd90f4ab8d08748bf225cdafa1f9d861.webm?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/cd90f4ab8d08748bf225cdafa1f9d861.mp4?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/67ccc8b11692edbca958fb9032caf3b0.avif?t=1753199962\" width=620 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为终极购物中心大亨！《购物中心经理模拟器》是一款深度管理游戏，在这里你可以建造和开发你自己的购物中心。你做出的每一个决定都会影响你的收入、访客数量和客户满意度。管理商店、处理广告、升级质量指数，并保持购物中心的整洁，才能在竞争中脱颖而出！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/030eb2a3c260319af5bb152fc5d99f32.avif?t=1753199962\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全面掌控</strong>：通过现代化的平板界面管理你整个购物中心！使用各种应用程序轻松跟踪收入、支出，并处理基本管理任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扩展店铺网络</strong>：从一个简单的商店开始，通过解锁和开设更多商店来扩展你的购物中心！每家商店都有自己的发展等级，随着游戏进展解锁新产品和家具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略性定价与顾客反应</strong>：为你的产品设定合适的价格，观察顾客的反应。如果价格太高，他们会离开，但如果找到合适的平衡，你的利润将飙升！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>广告收入和自动售货机</strong>：设置广告牌并在购物中心各处放置各种自动售货机。你吸引的访客越多，你的广告收入和销售额就越高！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/61158715f1e32ef7a4d80bef682d982b.poster.avif?t=1753199962\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/61158715f1e32ef7a4d80bef682d982b.webm?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092980/extras/61158715f1e32ef7a4d80bef682d982b.mp4?t=1753199962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态质量指数</strong>：通过植物和长椅等装饰元素提升购物中心的吸引力，以增加人流量和客户满意度。每个细节都对购物中心的成功至关重要！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>员工管理</strong>：雇佣销售助理、清洁工和自动售货机补货员！升级员工的能力使他们在处理任务时更高效、更快速。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全面的财务分析</strong>：通过中心图表监控你的购物中心的财务状况。查看每日收入和支出，以确保你为增长做出最佳战略决策。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战关卡和活动</strong>：完成各种任务并达到新等级，解锁令人兴奋的新功能。开设新店、安装更多广告牌，并升级购物中心的基础设施，让你的访客不断回流！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为什么你应该玩《购物中心经理模拟器》？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《购物中心经理模拟器》是一款丰富且引人入胜的管理游戏，挑战你的战略思维。一步一步地，你将开发你的购物中心，你做出的每一个决定都将塑造你的购物帝国的未来。你能成为最成功的购物中心经理，并建立城市最伟大的购物目的地吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入挑战，将你的购物中心变成购物天堂！立即下载《购物中心经理模拟器》，开始你成为镇上最佳购物中心经理的旅程！</p>",
